review_title: Terrible in connectivity, Keep getting disconnected/connected
reviews:
I was expecting to experience a real good quality Earphones but anytime I connect them to any of my devices (mp3 player, laptop or cellphone), they start getting disconnected and connected every 20-30 seconds. Not sure if this one has this issue or all of them?
The sounds quality is great and it's really comfortable for training and other activities. The only issue is connectivity.

I had no idea how it will work. Got it to connect to a TV as I'll be having a family staying with me for about 2 months.

One day after I got it, ordered 2 more for other TVs.
It's worth to have it!! The price is reasonable too.

Works amazing, I got what I was looking for. I'm using it every morning with no issues.
Strongly recommend to all!!
